 Neptune came from behind Darkmouse and shot at the bot that attacked her. 
Galvatron hovered in the air and went down and jumped on the back of the bot 
that grabbed  the cat. He was bigger then this bot and wrapped his arms 
around and squeezed as hard as he  could. His jewel on his chest powered up 
to send a blast through the bots defenseless back. "Let it down now or die."

--part1_127.39b7a73.28b92f80_boundary
